##If you’re aged 18 to 30

You may be able to live and work in the UK with an [India Young Professionals Scheme visa](/india-young-professionals-scheme-visa).

With this visa, you can:

+ work in the UK without a job offer
+ be self-employed and set up a company - as long as your premises are rented, your equipment is not worth more than £5,000 and you do not have any employees

###Eligibility

The eligibility criteria include:

+ being aged 18 to 30 when you apply
+ successfully applying for a ballot

###How long you can stay

Your visa can last for up to 2 years.  If you want to stay longer you must switch to another type of visa.
